Aldo Sambrell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aldo_Sambrell 0 Alfredo Sánchez Brell (23 February 1931 – 10 July 2010), known as Aldo Sambrell, was a Spanish actor, director, and producer who appeared in over 150 films between 1961 and 1996.
